- stateless (udp)
   -> no way to return a packet the same way it went back
- get acks
   -> resend, if not
   -> ping if not reachable
   -> mark text:
      red: not reached
      yellow: partial
      green: all


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Message-types:

- all with serial number?
- join channel request
- message
   * with or without channel
- ack
- noise
- forward packet (+ destination)
- infopacket
   * sends supported protocols:
      - I'm listening on ...
      - I can send via ...
   * send supported bandwidth
      - to calculate priority list
